(826, 0, 'Alteração Missão e Visão  e Políticas no site versão inglês', '2013-12-05 10:35:17', '2014-01-06 10:53:49', '2014-01-06 10:35:14', '2014-01-06 10:53:49', 648, 6, 648, 1, 'Computer', 378, 'Bom dia,\n\nRecentemente tivemos uma revisão em nossa Política de Qualidade e Meio Ambiente.\n\nAbaixo o texto em inglês para substituição no site:\n\nPOLÍTICA DE QUALIDADE\n\nQUALITY POLICY\n\nMeet our Client’s requirements.\nContinuously improve what we do, as to improve our Quality Management System.\nDevelop our Employees.\nSeek a harmonious relationship with the Environment and to suit the Work Safety and Hygiene conditions.\n\n\nPOLÍTICA DE MEIO AMBIENTE\n\nENVIRONMENT POLICY\n\n\nProduce Sugar Cane, Bioenergy, Sugar, Ethanol and Derivatives, with the minimum of environmental impact.\nReduce, Reuse, and Recycle the natural resources used and the residues generated in the Agroindustrial Process.\nEncourage actions which promote the environmental awareness for a sustainable activity.\n\nPeço também a substituição de Nossa Missão e Visão:\n\nOUR MISSION\n	\nOur mission is to produce and trade Sugar Cane, Bioenergy, Quality Ethanol and Sugar, in a sustainable way, with profitability and excellence, satisfying our Clients, Share Holders and Employees.\n\nOUR VISION\n\nTo be recognized and admired by the market and society as a Model Enterprise and quality reference for our products and service.\n\nPeço também que incluam a História da empresa:\n\nENTERPRISE\n\nThe Usina Ester is one of the landmarks of the regional development; it is one of the oldest Sugar Mills in the State of São Paulo, in activity. It is a Regional Enterprise, whose history, in many occasions inserts itself  in the Brazilian History, of our State, of our region, through its origin, due to the innovations introduced, through their Owners, who during all this time have participated from many political, cultural and sports events in the Country.\nThe Enterprise was founded on 2 March 1898 the name (Ester) was given to honor Sr. Paulo de Almeida Nogueira’s wife, Sra. Esther Nogueira.\nIts main founders were;\n \n Arthur Nogueira; \n Paulo de Almeida Nogueira; \n José Paulino Nogueira; \n Sidrack Nogueira; \n Antonio Carlos Silva Telles; \n\nThe Usina Ester manufactures Sugar and Ethanol with the highest quality standard. It owns well equipped labs and skilled people as to ensure a rigorous control and monitoring of its Products, which are produced as from sugar cane. It is more than 115 years of tradition in the sugar and alcohol market.\n\n\nMain products;\n \nETHANOL\nNeutral \nIndustrial \n\nALCOHOLIC DISTILLATED \n\n\nVHP SUGAR\n\n\nObrigada!\n', 3, 3, 3, 162, 2, 3, '&lt;p&gt;Removido conforme solicitado, favor verificar.&lt;/p&gt;', 'none', 0, 0, '2014-01-07 17:39:00', '2014-01-06 10:35:14', 0, 1988466, 777446, 776331, 343774, 0, 0, 0),
